    "encrypted": "false",
    "long_instructions": "## Tell an Expository Data Story with AI\r\n\r\nUse AI Chat to analyze the Spotify data cards and tell an expository data story.\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\nDo This:\r\n1. Upload the **PDF file** of the Spotify data cards from the library by selecting **Upload > From Library**.\r\n2. Ask AI Chat one of these questions:\r\n   - *What data attributes might be considered for a user who receives the [insert card name] card?*\r\n   - *Help me to brainstorm some data attributes that Spotify might keep on its users.*\r\n   - *I am considering focusing on [list data attributes], what interesting title might I give my card?*",
